OL,3,CUber rolls out 'senior accounts' in UK
OL,4,Cto help elderly people travel
OL,6,FUber is launching a feature for
OL,7,Frelatives to remotely book and track
OL,8,Ftrips for their elderly parents or
OL,9,Fgrandparents in the UK.
OL,11,FNew "senior accounts" are designed to
OL,12,Fmake it easier for order people to use
OL,13,Fthe ride-hailing app to get around.
OL,15,FIt gives people access to a
OL,16,Fstreamlined version of the app
OL,17,Ffeaturing larger text, buttons that
OL,18,Fare easier to tap, simplified screens
OL,19,Fand fewer steps to making a booking.
