OL,3,CUber rolls out 'senior accounts' in UK
OL,4,Cto help elderly people travel
OL,6,FThrough Uber's existing "family
OL,7,Fprofiles" feature, trusted family
OL,8,Fmembers or caregivers can invite an
OL,9,Folder adult to set up an account.
OL,11,FThey can then remotely book or manage
OL,12,Frides for the older user.
OL,14,FIt means they can offer support from
OL,15,Fafar including live-tracking their
OL,16,Ftrip and the ability to contact the
OL,17,Fdriver or Uber's safety reporting line.
OL,19,FLoved ones will also be able to access
OL,20,Fthe driver's name and vehicle
OL,21,Finformation when a booking is made.
