OL,3,CUber rolls out 'senior accounts' in UK
OL,4,Cto help elderly people travel
OL,6,FUsers can save favourite places for
OL,7,Fbooking shortcuts, or use flexible
OL,8,Fpayment options ` and they also have
OL,9,Fthe option to book trips independently
OL,10,Fwithout linking to a relative.
OL,12,FSenior accounts were piloted in the US
OL,13,Fand Latin America last month and will
OL,14,Fnow will be rolled out in the UK.
