OL,3,CUber rolls out 'senior accounts' in UK
OL,4,Cto help elderly people travel
OL,6,FUber said it worked with older users
OL,7,Fand accessibility advocates to develop
OL,8,Fthe feature, which was designed to
OL,9,Faddress concerns that many elderly
OL,10,Fpeople feel excluded from technology
OL,11,For do not have the skills to be
OL,12,Fdigitally-savvy.
OL,14,FIt also follows the launch of "teen
OL,15,Faccounts" last year where parents and
OL,16,Fcarers can also supervise bookings and
OL,17,Fteenagers are matched to more
OL,18,Fexperienced drivers.
