OL,3,CUber rolls out 'senior accounts' in UK
OL,4,Cto help elderly people travel
OL,6,FUber UK's general manager Andrew Brem
OL,7,Fsaid the tools "prioritise simplicity,
OL,8,Fsafety and peace of mind" for older
OL,9,Fpeople and their families.
OL,11,F"These features are all about helping
OL,12,Folder adults stay independent and
OL,13,Fconnected, while giving loved ones the
OL,14,Fconfidence that Uber is there to
OL,15,Fhelp," he said.
